collections.name: TacoVerse
collections.description:
TacoVerse is a unique collection where tacos are more than just delicious fillings in a shell! They’re characters with their own personalities, adventures, and quirks! Each taco in this vibrant collection is a one-of-a-kind creation, designed in a fun way with expressions that bring them to life. 

In TacoVerse, every taco has its own story. From the adventurous “Spicy Senorita” who just loves to explore the TacoUniverse, up to “Sir Guac-a-lot,” a laid-back taco who’s always chilling in the background. The possibilities are endless. Whether they’re embarking on taco-tastic journeys, cracking jokes, or simply living their best taco life, each character has its own flavor of fun.

Inspired by the iconic mind of MrCoinDogs, TacoVerse isn’t just a collection of NFTs - it’s an ever-growing universe of Taco Characters, each with their own hobbies, passions, and stories to tell. So, get ready to dive into a world where tacos are not just food, they’re a way of life. Welcome to the TacoVerse!

collections.name: Bastien Bouta NFT collection
collections.description:
My name is Bastien Bouta, a self-taught artist and creator of Aplotica Studio. I began my artistic journey designing minimalist tattoos. Over time, my style evolved into vibrant geometric abstract minimalism, always emphasizing simplicity and balance.

I draw inspiration from artists like Picasso, Matisse, Malevich, Herbin, and movements such as Fauvism, Cubism, and the elegance of Japanese Ukiyo-e art. These influences shape my works, created both on canvas and digitally.

Through NFTs, I offer exclusive digital art. Each piece is unique, ensuring authenticity and ownership via the blockchain. Collectors can download high-resolution files and print them locally, promoting an eco-conscious approach to art collection.

For those new to NFTs, the process is straightforward—artworks can be purchased and owned digitally, providing a modern way to enjoy and invest in art.
